  <?dbhtml filename="xextproto.html"?>

  <title>xextproto-&xextproto-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This packages provides development headers describing the wire protocol
      for various extensions, the client-side libraries of which are provided in
      the Xext library.
    </para>

